# ChatBuddy - 3D LLM Chat Interface

A Next.js application that combines LLM chat capabilities with Three.js 3D visualization.

## Features

- Real-time chat with Llama 2 LLM
- 3D visualization of chat messages using Three.js
- Streaming responses
- Interactive 3D camera controls

## Setup

1. Install dependencies:
```bash
npm install
```

2. Run the development server:
```bash
npm run dev
```

3. Make sure you have Ollama running locally with Llama 2 model installed.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 13+
- React Three Fiber
- Three.js
- TypeScript
- Ollama
